//            max({L.maxSub,R.maxSub,L.maxSuf+R.maxPre}),
//            L.total+R.total }; }

// Two lazy types â€” multiply THEN add (order matters):
// apply multiply first; compose: if assign arrives, overwrite; if add arrives, add to existing</pre>

